  "detailed_description": "<h1>About us</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We will continue to update the game and improve the gaming experience. Thank you for your support and patience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wish you all a happy game！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >—— “Survivors Of The Zombie World” Developer: Kt&Tata</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survivors Of The Zombie World is a 3D pixel-style zombie survival game. Survivors fight in a world full of zombies, looking for food, ammunition, medicine and other supplies on the map and trying to survive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆ Current Features◆ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/ae102baa21d3b6aecd359e66f2f2c71a.poster.avif?t=1770495326\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/ae102baa21d3b6aecd359e66f2f2c71a.webm?t=1770495326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/ae102baa21d3b6aecd359e66f2f2c71a.mp4?t=1770495326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----3D pixel survival shooting game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/d2693db7b2a018fdfafabdc14bccc0a7.poster.avif?t=1770495326\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/d2693db7b2a018fdfafabdc14bccc0a7.webm?t=1770495326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/d2693db7b2a018fdfafabdc14bccc0a7.mp4?t=1770495326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----Story mode: Contains 40+ levels, you can clear the zombies to pass the level, you need to escape to the destination, you need to collect some items. Various small easter eggs are waiting for you to discover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/8ac66858508b6e91ff43ff02a74a07e1.poster.avif?t=1770495326\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/8ac66858508b6e91ff43ff02a74a07e1.webm?t=1770495326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/8ac66858508b6e91ff43ff02a74a07e1.mp4?t=1770495326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----Survival mode: You need to survive in various terrains. Time is long, and you need to find something to eat when you are hungry. If you run out of ammunition, you need to find supplies. It is too dark at night, you have to turn on the flashlight, or hide in a safe corner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/3a74b54019d1a1b41d8750c1c0df0f87.poster.avif?t=1770495326\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/3a74b54019d1a1b41d8750c1c0df0f87.webm?t=1770495326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/3a74b54019d1a1b41d8750c1c0df0f87.mp4?t=1770495326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----Defense mode: A large wave of zombies rush into the base, and you must pick up weapons to protect the last piece of land. There are electric towers around the door, which can protect you, but you must pay attention to maintenance and pick up supplies in time. Zombies are getting stronger and stronger, I wish you good luck!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/addf1a9329983ca399aeff6b66fd6264.poster.avif?t=1770495326\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/addf1a9329983ca399aeff6b66fd6264.webm?t=1770495326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/addf1a9329983ca399aeff6b66fd6264.mp4?t=1770495326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----Temporarily supports LAN online mode, and survive with your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----More than 20 survivors can be chosen, and they have their own characteristics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/f0c4d677536c7fad90b6b6f546e62ee6.poster.avif?t=1770495326\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/f0c4d677536c7fad90b6b6f546e62ee6.webm?t=1770495326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985910/extras/f0c4d677536c7fad90b6b6f546e62ee6.mp4?t=1770495326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
